      public BasicInfo()

    • BasicInfo

      public BasicInfo(String hospitalID, String role) throws Exception
      Constructs a BasicInfo object for a user with the specified hospital ID and role.
      Parameters:
      hospitalID - The ID of the hospital account.
      role - The role of the user (e.g., patient, doctor, pharmacist).
      Throws:
      Exception - if the hospital ID is not found.
